// Brute-Force RDP Attack Hunt
// Surfaces top attacking IPs by failed login count (EventID 4625) in the last 24 hours
// Run in: Microsoft Sentinel → Logs

SecurityEvent
| where TimeGenerated > ago(1d)
| where EventID == 4625                          // Failed logon
| summarize Count=count() by IpAddress, Computer
| where Count >= 15                              // Threshold: adjust as needed
| order by Count desc
